    &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.mobileread.com/forums/showthread.php?t=62831&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;Review - mobileread&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.mobileread.com/forums/showthread.php?t=48655&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;Customiza&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o - comics e slideshow - mobileread&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
